{"tid":503582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"讓座予有需要人士? 廢話黎","createTime":"2017-12-19T04:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T04:32:29.000Z","uid":147961,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02ec43fe48971c2789a09e0ca70bf7b8d78629a4","tid":503582,"uid":147961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/120051_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F120051_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=467ccc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先搭地鐵見到既   有個後生仔隻腳整親拎住助行器都無人讓座   反而d廢老行得走得都好鍾意扮可憐要人讓座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e230f6c9acc653a3cac7c8f755b7aef32fdaafd","tid":503582,"uid":43924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"尋日坐地都鐵，門一開條廢即刻狗衝入黎，見附近冇位一路向前行，最後仲開口話腰痛叫人讓俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n坐少陣洗死咩？要坐就坐巴士啦，再唔係咪撚出街，係屋企坐到死囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過咁，有得坐好坐啦，過多兩年想坐都冇得坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝廢老全部生癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93ea74f40ff7c74b67c0969eccd86b4df042307","tid":503582,"uid":147961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"連登無人關心後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}